metadata.name: Cloud paste
metadata.description:
Have you ever seen a toothpaste-like cloud as a kid?
What you see in this photo is like real toothpaste.  However, if you look closely, toothpaste is a cloud in the sky.  
This photo is a miracle photo taken without compositing.

This photo received 180,000 likes and 9.4 million impressions.
